-----------------------------------------------------------------

Icecast's various components have been installed in the following
directories:

  - The icecast server:
    %%PREFIX%%/sbin/icecast

  - Icecast configuration files have been installed in:
    %%PREFIX%%/etc/icecast/

  - Icecast documentation is located in:
    %%PREFIX%%/share/doc/icecast/

-----------------------------------------------------------------
